<p>This site is built with <a href="https://jekyllrb.com" target="_blank">Jekyll</a>, stored in <a href="https://www.github.com" target="_blank">Github</a> and hosted by <a href="https://www.netlify.com" target="_blank">Netlify</a>.</p>

